  "body": "When collector was running I've changed the ES cluster. As a result an index was created with incorrect mapping - \r\n```\r\n{\r\n    \"jaeger-span-2017-09-03\": {\r\n        \"mappings\": {\r\n            \"span\": {\r\n                \"properties\": {\r\n\r\n                    (removed for brevity)\r\n\r\n                    \"traceID\": {\r\n                        \"fields\": {\r\n                            \"keyword\": {\r\n                                \"ignore_above\": 256,\r\n                                \"type\": \"keyword\"\r\n                            }\r\n                        },\r\n                        \"type\": \"text\"\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI suspect that setting `dynamic=false` on the top-level tocument or `action.auto_create_index: false` would solve the problem.",
